org.eclipse.paho.client.mqttv3

Interface MqttCallbackExtended

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MqttCallback

    public interface MqttCallbackExtended
extends MqttCallback
    Extension of MqttCallback to allow new callbacks without breaking the API for existing applications. Classes implementing this interface can be registered on both types of client: IMqttClient.setCallback(MqttCallback) and IMqttAsyncClient.setCallback(MqttCallback)
